# ☕ Coffee Shop Sales Analysis – Power BI Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes sales data from a coffee shop and presents insights using an **interactive Power BI dashboard**.  
The goal is to identify key sales trends, understand customer behavior, and provide actionable insights to improve business performance.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze **daily, weekly, and monthly sales trends**  
- Identify **top-selling products and categories**  
- Track **sales by location, product type, and time of day**  
- Provide **KPIs** (Revenue, Transactions, Avg. Bill Size) for quick decision-making  
- Create interactive dashboards with **filters and slicers** for deep exploration  

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- **Power BI** – Data visualization & dashboard building  
- **Excel/CSV** – Data source for raw sales data  
- **DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)** – For custom KPIs and calculations  
- **Data Cleaning & Transformation** – Performed using Power Query  

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features
- **KPIs Overview**: Total Revenue, No. of Transactions, Avg. Sales per Transaction  
- **Sales Trends**: Line charts showing sales over time  
- **Top Products**: Best-selling coffee types & categories  
- **Location Analysis**: Revenue distribution across different stores  
- **Customer Insights**: Time-based purchase behavior (morning vs. evening sales)  
- **Filters & Slicers**: Interactive controls for product type, date range, and store location  

---

